ssary temporal dependences to\nsupport such a state in full M-theory. We also discuss how our analysis points\ntowards a surprising connection to the four-dimensional null energy condition,\nfor a Friedman-Lemaitre-Robertson-Walker state in the IIB side, as a\nconsistency condition for the existence of an effective field theory\ndescription in M-theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2021 19:44:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Sep 2021 11:23:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-23"}
