problem that\ncan be efficiently solved by a stochastic expectation maximization (EM)\nalgorithm. Experiments on multiple benchmark datasets of FL show that our\nmethod outperforms several popular baseline methods. The experimental source\ncodes are publicly available on the Github repository\nhttps://github.com/mingxuts/multi-center-fed-learning .\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Aug 2021 12:20:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 21 Aug 2021 05:51:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2023 02:24:59 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 02:25:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-01"}
